## Use a block definition which varies in length
. tests/setup

cat <<'EOF' >"$TEST_INPUT"
* Title

** Subtitle

Set the variable =greeting= to "hello".

#+begin_src sh
  greeting=hello
#+end_src

Use greeting.

#+begin_src sh
  echo "$greeting!"
